<article class="project-content">
  <header>
    <h1>Art Direction</h1>
    <h4>Illustration and Graphic Design</h4>
  </header>
    <section class="columns02d mb1em">
    <p>My design aesthetic is brand-focused and clean. I strive to portray the essence of my client's brand to the best of my ability.</p>
      
    <p>I build simple visual vocabularies to guide visitors into the brand experience. A limited color palette helps to personify the brand.</p>
      
    <p>I like images that provoke an emotional response and are memorable. Images that don't provide easy answers create a space for conversation and dialog, allowing the viewer to fill in the story, ponder, and identify with the brand.</p>
      
    <p>I work with sumi ink, pencil, egg tempera, Photoshop and Adobe Illustrator. I know the code when it comes to HTML and CSS. </p>

    <p>As an artist, I enjoy trying new things, delving into creative journeys of scientific exploration and invention.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="projectthumbs">
    <ul class="cards">
      <li class="cards__item" id="05">
        <div class="card">
