            <div class="card__image card__image--maxdelivery"></div></a>
          <div class="card__content">
            <h4 class="card__title01">Max Delivery</h4>
            <p class="card__text">Craig Webb concieved, wrote and designed this edgy brand-launch ad campaign to introduce Maxdelivery to Tribeca.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="cards__item" id="03">
        <div class="card">
          <a href="graphicprojects/graphic-project_03.htm" title="Iridium" onclick="document.getElementById('modal1').style.display='block'" target="iframe_modal">
            <div class="card__image card__image--iridium"></div></a>
          <div class="card__content">
            <h4 class="card__title01">Iridium Telephone ad campaign</h4>
            <p class="card__text">Craig Webb worked on the Iridium campaign from inception until demise, helping to coordinate the campaign.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="cards__item" id="06">
        <div class="card">
          <a href="graphicprojects/graphic-project_06.htm" title="Honda Accord" onclick="document.getElementById('modal1').style.display='block'" target="iframe_modal">
